---
import BaseLayout from "../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro";
import EstimateModal from "../components/ui/EstimateModal";
import { business } from "../data/business";

const springServices = [
  "Storm damage cleanup and broken branch removal",
  "Deadwood pruning and crown cleaning",
  "Deep root fertilization to jumpstart growth",
  "Preventive pest and disease treatments (Emerald Ash Borer, bark beetles, etc.)",
  "Tree health assessments after winter stress",
  "Brush chipping and yard debris cleanup",
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Spring Cleanup & Treatments | Arbor Care Denver CO"
  description="Spring cleanup and tree treatments in Denver, CO. Post-winter storm damage cleanup, pruning, fertilization, and pest prevention. Call (303) 949-6818."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[500px] md:min-h-[60vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
    <img src="/assets/hero-services.webp" alt="Spring cleanup and tree treatment services in Denver CO" class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover" width="1920" height="1080" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60"></div>
    <div class="container relative z-10 py-20 pb-28 md:py-28 text-center">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <div class="mx-auto mb-6 inline-flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-accent/20">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.9C15.5 4.9 17 3.5 19 2c1 2 2 4.5 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z"/><path d="M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white md:text-5xl leading-tight">
          Spring Cleanup &amp; Treatments
          <span class="block text-accent mt-2 text-xl md:text-2xl">Get Your Property Ready for the Season</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 text-lg text-white/90 max-w-2xl">
          Winter takes a toll on Denver trees. Spring is the time to clean up storm damage, treat emerging pest issues, and set your trees up for a healthy growing season.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
          <a href={business.phoneTel} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-accent-foreground shadow-lg hover:bg-accent/90 transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            Call {business.phone}
          </a>
          <EstimateModal client:load className="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-white/15 backdrop-blur border border-white/30 px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white hover:bg-white/25 transition-colors">
            Get Free Estimate
          </EstimateModal>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-primary/95 backdrop-blur-sm">
      <div class="container flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-2 py-3 text-sm text-primary-foreground">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
          <span class="font-medium">100+ Five-Star Reviews</span>
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M15.477 12.89 17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"/></svg>
          <span class="font-medium">ISA-Certified Arborists</span>
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z"/></svg>
          <span class="font-medium">Free Estimates</span>
        </span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          <span class="font-medium">Family Owned</span>
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold md:text-4xl mb-6">Spring Is When Problems Show Up — And When You Can Fix Them</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          After a Denver winter, trees reveal the damage - broken branches from heavy snow, deadwood that wasn't visible before, and pest issues that start ramping up as temperatures rise. Spring is the best window to address all of it before the growing season is underway.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Our Spring Services</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
          {springServices.map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 text-accent mt-1 shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.9C15.5 4.9 17 3.5 19 2c1 2 2 4.5 2 8 0 5.5-4.78 10-10 10Z"/><path d="M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12"/></svg>
              <span>{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Why Spring Treatments Matter</h3>
        <p class="leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          Many pest treatments are most effective when applied preventively in spring — before insects are actively causing damage. Emerald Ash Borer trunk injections, for example, need to be applied before the beetles emerge. Once a tree shows heavy damage from EAB, treatment options narrow significantly. Spring is also the ideal time for deep root fertilization, which gives trees the nutrient boost they need to recover from winter stress and push healthy new growth.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-muted">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl rounded-xl border-2 border-accent/30 bg-card p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold md:text-3xl">Schedule Your Spring Cleanup</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Call for a free assessment. We'll walk your property, identify what needs attention, and give you a firm quote.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8">
          <a href={business.phoneTel} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-accent-foreground shadow-lg hover:bg-accent/90 transition-colors">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            {business.phone}
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
